snippet.title: 🔴 Being a Developer isn't only about Coding | Amber Wilson
snippet.description:
Amber is a frontend engineer living in Berlin and working at N26. She organises and coaches at a coding workshop called codebar. She likes writing about accessibility, the JAM Stack, and dev tips. She believes the web is for everyone and loves being part of the web community.

She will talk about - Being a Developer isn't only about Coding.

Watch LIVE 
👉 at 6:00 PM (Central European Time)
👉 on Thursday 28th January, 2021

Enjoy 🌸
